  "5-15": (
    caption: [and Figure 5–16). These regions occur routinely on the lagging-strand template, and if not removed, they can impede the DNA synthesis catalyzed by DNA polymerase. A Sliding Ring Holds a Moving DNA Polymerase onto the DNA],
