  "5-16": (
    caption: [Human single-strand binding protein bound to DNA. (A) Front view of the two DNA-binding domains of the protein (called RPA), which cover a total of eight nucleotides. Note that the DNA bases remain exposed in this protein–DNA complex. (B) Diagram showing the three-dimensional structure, with the DNA strand (orange) viewed end on. (PDB code: 1JMC.)],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
