  "5-24": (
    caption: [is fundamentally the same for bacteria and eukaryotes, the detailed way in which this process is performed and regulated differs considerably between these two groups of organisms. We first consider the case in bacteria and then turn to the more complex situation found in yeasts, mammals, and other eukaryotes.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
