  "5-37": (
    caption: [A summary of spontaneous alterations that require DNA repair. The sites on each nucleotide modified by spontaneous oxidative damage (red arrows), hydrolytic attack (blue arrows), and methylation (green arrows) are shown, with the width of each arrow indicating the relative frequency of each event (see Table 5–3). (After T. Lindahl, Nature 362:709–715, 1993.)],
